      </center></td>
      <td><center>
      <p>yes clips, narrator - all feeding into main theme - expert opinion</p>
      </center></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>novelty</th>
      <td><center>
      <p>yes - after time</p>
      </center></td>
      <td><center>
      <p>yes - new twist on old themes</p>
      </center></td>
      <td><center>
      <p>can be - underwater photography, unusual topics and investigators</p>
      </center></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</blockquote>

